{"tid":1773112,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"［養貓高手請進］貓咪有咁既症狀係唔係有問題","createTime":"2019-12-07T08:16:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-07T10:52:21.000Z","uid":99032,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c093961957a356bb705aebe6adb4aec902a3d096","tid":1773112,"uid":99032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T08:16:38.000Z","msg":"代人問 因為朋友冇帳<br />\n<br />\n由前幾日天氣開始轉涼開始<br />\n貓貓已經慢慢咁好似突然180度唔同曬<br />\n平時會識自己去廁所 <br />\n到前幾日會突然有好幾次屙落其他地方（枕頭 床辱 同埋主人訓訓下覺會突然屙落佢個頭到）<br />\n鬧完幾次之後到尋日<br />\n佢又冇周圍屙 會去返自己個廁所<br />\n但係會去得勁密<br />\n15-20分鐘一次 覺得有啲唔同所以去睇下<br />\n但係去睇又唔係好多排泄物<br />\n<br />\n利申 貓咪平時食野飲水又同平時差唔多（濕糧 餅乾 水機都有 好小食零食）<br />\n多謝巴絲打肯睇曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9db93d653b41307088ac58fb8e90137b86c480f9","tid":1773112,"uid":2612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T08:17:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">128 維園見</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tM1AHsT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtM1AHsT.jpg&h=51b9806f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nZ3GC1d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnZ3GC1d.jpg&h=a58f11cd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e3czX1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe3czX1e.jpg&h=afb0dc00&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JMAmC1f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJMAmC1f.jpg&h=565489c9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OQkE87V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOQkE87V.jpg&h=ca6df116&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7ae34883e2bb3124f92a6fb508adbfb974a43e82","tid":1773112,"uid":230536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T08:30:19.000Z","msg":"習慣突然之間改變就身體有唔舒服，直接帶佢去睇醫生啦"},{"pid":"3e2a826a1244c22337d557188ed054730653a3a0","tid":1773112,"uid":211900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T08:32:37.000Z","msg":"你估淨係啲貓貓狗狗係咁咩 係咁屙但係次次都屙少少 <br />\n而家好多人都係咁㗎 所以我懷疑根本就係嗰啲催淚彈污染左啲食水或者嘢食"},{"pid":"eab9315ce8f81d6f5b4dede279a6cbc77c5cee79","tid":1773112,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T08:34:19.000Z","msg":"餵多啲濕糧"},{"pid":"e9c323b3630d94c414eeacb71f6428b711bb0a8b","tid":1773112,"uid":79355,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T08:35:17.000Z","msg":"貓唔去番廁所痾已經係有問題<br />\n睇醫生啦"},{"pid":"8bbc711a3ba0ca1b4f1f9cb7960eca556290e22b","tid":1773112,"uid":136537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T10:52:21.000Z","msg":"有機會尿道炎 帶佢睇下醫生啦<br />\n有個安心都好"}]}